page.title: 13Biography(1)
page.content: My alarm goes off at 7:00am.I get dressed and go downstairs.I feed the ponies and let the ducks out while Mum is getting the breakfast.I have cereal or a boiled egg.I pack my books and we leave for school taking my sister into Ross to get a lift to her school. Sometimes we do shopping on the way. School starts at 9:15am.We do Maths and English then we have a break and then work until lunchtime.We often have chips,fish fingers and beans and for pudding we have mousse.At 1:05pm we start work again,we have Geography and Games and at 3:15pm I go home. At 5:30pm I have my tea then I go riding on my pony and I walk the dog.I go and watch television for a while till bedtime at 9:00pm.But by the time I get in bed it's usually later.
